<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000438/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Examination
Description. The final exam will consist of exercises focusing on at least two of the thematic blocks (units) of the course.
Qualification criteria. Each examination exercise is valued from 0 to 10. The exam grade will be the arithmetic average of the grade obtained in the exercises that form the exam as long as the grades corresponding to each of them are above or equal 3.5.
Moment and place: To be determined by the Head of Studies in due course."""@es ;
    ns1:hasEvaluationTrial <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000438/2025-26/evaluation/trial1>,
